<item>
            <title>[LU-18136] Remove LDLM_LOCK_* macros (and other LDLM cruft)</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-18136</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;These macros simply reference their function counterparts.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
@@
expression x;
@@
- LDLM_LOCK_PUT(x)
+ ldlm_lock_put(x)
@@
expression x;
@@
- LDLM_LOCK_RELEASE(x)
+ ldlm_lock_put(x)
@@
expression x;
@@
- LDLM_LOCK_GET(x)
+ ldlm_lock_get(x) &lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
